room_title: Escape room "Into the Assassin's Lair" by The Cryptic Room in Omaha
room_address: 523 S Main St Council Bluffs, IA 51503
room_description: Following up on an anonymous tip about suspicious activity at an abandoned warehouse, your team finds an office that is clearly not abandoned. While looking around, you realize that you are in the midst of what you suspect is the lair of an international assassin. As you investigate scene, you hear the door slam shut - you realize you are trapped and the timer on the bomb is ticking… Can you figure out who the assassin’s next victim is before the next attack? Can you make it out of the warehouse before the timer runs out?
